# ====================================================================
# cMATRA Mainnet Mint Ceremony — Locked Parameters
# ====================================================================
# Generated 2026-05-18 by `aiken blueprint apply` against the audited
# source at flux_mint_policy commit 79de97e (PR #3) + claim_validator
